OL,3,CNine men arrested in Bradford as part
OL,4,Cof crackdown on illegal working trade
OL,6,FOver 500 arrests and 600 enforcement
OL,7,Fvisits have been carried out across
OL,8,Fthe North East, Yorkshire and the
OL,9,FHumber in a crackdown on the illegal
OL,10,Fworking trade in the UK.
OL,12,FSince the 5 July last year, to 31 May,
OL,13,F687 visits resulted in 557 arrests,
OL,14,Fmarking a 14% and 56% rise
OL,15,Frespectively compared to the year
OL,16,Fbefore.
OL,18,FThe action forms part of a nationwide
OL,19,Fintensification which has seen illegal
OL,20,Fworking visits increase by 48% and
OL,21,Farrests spike by 51% across the UK.
