OL,3,CNine men arrested in Bradford as part
OL,4,Cof crackdown on illegal working trade
OL,6,FIn a joint operation in March with
OL,7,FWest Yorkshire Police, government
OL,8,Fofficers visited the junction of
OL,9,FNaples Street and Whetley Lane in
OL,10,FBradford.
OL,12,FThey were acting on intelligence that
OL,13,Fillegal workers were being collected
OL,14,Fdaily by vans transporting them to
OL,15,Fwork.
