OL,3,CNine men arrested in Bradford as part
OL,4,Cof crackdown on illegal working trade
OL,6,FOfficers intercepted the group waiting
OL,7,Fat the hotspot to be collected for
OL,8,Fwork in the morning and arrested nine
OL,9,Fmen, including six Afghans, one
OL,10,FNigerian, one Bangladeshi and one
OL,11,FEthiopian.
OL,13,FThe Home Office say that in many
OL,14,Fcases, individuals travelling to the
OL,15,FUK illegally are sold a lie by
OL,16,Fsmuggling gangs that they will be able
OL,17,Fto live and work freely in the UK.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
