OL,3,CNine men arrested in Bradford as part
OL,4,Cof crackdown on illegal working trade
OL,6,FHowever, in reality they often end up
OL,7,Ffacing squalid living conditions,
OL,8,Fminimal pay and inhumane working
OL,9,Fhours, with the threat of arrest and
OL,10,Fremoval if they are caught working
OL,11,Fillegally.
OL,13,FThe government are now extending Right
OL,14,Fto Work checks on those hiring gig
OL,15,Feconomy and zero-hours workers in
OL,16,Fsectors like construction, food
OL,17,Fdelivery, beauty salons and courier
OL,18,Fservices.
