OL,3,CNine men arrested in Bradford as part
OL,4,Cof crackdown on illegal working trade
OL,6,FMinister for Border Security and
OL,7,FAsylum, Dame Angela Eagle, said:
OL,8,F"Illegal working undermines our border
OL,9,Fsecurity, damages our economy and
OL,10,Foften leads to the exploitation of
OL,11,Fvulnerable migrants.
OL,13,F"This activity will no longer be
OL,14,Ftolerated on our watch and these
OL,15,Ffigures demonstrate this government's
OL,16,Fdetermination to disrupt organised
OL,17,Fimmigration criminals at every level."
